               <h1 class="c-heading c-heading--50" style="color: #006ea1;">What is VoIP</h1>
               <div class="c-grid c-grid--halves">
                  <div class="c-grid__item">
                     <div class="u-content">
                        <p class="lead">
                        <p class="c-paragraph c-paragraph--lead">VoIP is an abbreviation for Voice over IP and it simply means calling over a data network.</p>
                        </p>
                        <figure class="c-media c-media--image"><a href=""><img loading="lazy" class="alignleft size-full wp-image-9431" src="https://www.voys.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/WebPic7.png" alt="VoIP connect via a data network" width="800" height="97" srcset="https://www.voys.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/WebPic7.png 800w, https://www.voys.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/WebPic7-300x36.png 300w, https://www.voys.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/WebPic7-768x93.png 768w, https://www.voys.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/WebPic7-100x12.png 100w, https://www.voys.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/WebPic7-250x30.png 250w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" /></a></figure>
                        <p>Calling over a data network, or internet connection, has some great advantages. Flexibility and <strong>savings of 30 to 60% </strong>on operational telephone costs, are generally seen as the most important benefits.</p>
                     </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="c-grid__item">
                     <div class="u-content">
                        <h2>Benefits of switching to VoIP include</h2>
                        <ul class="advantages">
                           <li>Easy and cheap to set up</li>
                           <li>Corporate functionality, but at small business costs</li>
                           <li>Pay only for the services you need</li>
                           <li>Retain your old phone number or get a new one</li>
                           <li>Scales with your business</li>
                           <li>Work from anywhere</li>
                        </ul>
                        <%--<p>Read more about the other <a href="/voip/advantages-of-voip/">benefits of Voice over IP</a>?</p>--%>
                     </div>
                  </div>
               </div>
            </div>
         </div>
