                              <div class="c-card__content   ">
                                 <h2 class="c-heading c-heading--30">#1 A reliable Internet connection</h2>
                                 <p>To switch to VoIP, first of all you will need a reliable and fast internet connection. This can be a mobile connection such as LTE, or fixed technologies such as ADSL, fiber, wireless WAN etc. To find out if your internet connection is sufficient, please <a href="contact.aspx">contact us</a>. We're happy to discuss all the possibilities with you.</p>
                              </div>
                           </div>
                        </li>
                        <li class="c-grid__item c-card ">
                           <div class="c-card__container ">
                              <div class="c-card__image" style="background-image: url('https://www.voys.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/AT-767x450.jpg')"></div>
                              <div class="c-card__content   ">
                                 <h2 class="c-heading c-heading--30">#2 VoIP hardware</h2>
                                 <p> To tap into the full potential of VoIP, you will want to use special <a href="phone.aspx">IP phones</a>. They look similar to traditional business phones, but often have extra features. Important is that the phone supports the 'SIP protocol'. You also get <a href="phone.aspx">cordless IP phones</a> and devices that enable you to connect your analog phone to our network.</p>
                              </div>
                           </div>
                        </li>
                        <li class="c-grid__item c-card ">
                           <div class="c-card__container ">
                              <div class="c-card__image" style="background-image: url('https://www.voys.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/ab-767x450.jpg')"></div>
                              <div class="c-card__content   ">
                                 <h2 class="c-heading c-heading--30">#3 A Subscription</h2>
                                 <p>Subscribe to <a title="Voys" href="tour.aspx">one of our services</a>. For as little as R170 a month you can enjoy a professional phone system with all the bells and whistles. You can be ready to start calling within one day. Plus, you can cancel anytime you want. Enjoy maximum flexibility, with no strings attached.</p>
